{% doc %}
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   DESIGN TOKENS — Master Loader
   Renders all 21 foundation token systems as CSS custom
   properties on :root for global use across all sections,
   blocks, snippets, and templates.
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

   Token categories:
    1.  Typography Scale
    2.  Font Pairing System
    3.  Color Palette System     (in color-palette.liquid)
    4.  Semantic Color Tokens
    5.  Spacing Scale
    6.  Border Radius Scale
    7.  Shadow System
    8.  Border System
    9.  Opacity Tokens
    10. Z-Index Layers
    11. Animation Tokens
    12. Transition Tokens
    13. Grid System
    14. Breakpoints
    15. Container Widths
    16. Icon System
    17. Illustration System
    18. Image Ratio System
    19. Elevation System
    20. Theme Presets
    21. Padding & Margin System

   Usage: {% render 'design-tokens' %}
{% enddoc %}

{%- comment -%}
  Load all design token systems as modular snippets.
  Each file outputs {% style %} blocks with CSS custom properties on :root.
  This keeps the token system maintainable and individually overridable.
{%- endcomment -%}

